      "value": "{\"Create Batch\":\"batch\",\"List Batches\":\"batch\",\"Retrieve Batch\":\"batch\",\"Cancel Batch\":\"batch\",\"Get Batch Results\":\"batch\",\"Upload File\":\"file\",\"List Files\":\"file\",\"Get File Content\":\"file\",\"Delete File\":\"file\"}",
      "type": "string"
    }
